<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>미션 수정 | 갓생 업</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white border-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/main">갓생 업</a>
        <a href="/main" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm">메인으로</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<main class="container py-4 py-lg-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
            <section class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <p class="text-secondary text-uppercase small mb-2">Edit Mission</p>
                        <h1 class="h3 mb-2">미션 수정</h1>
                        <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">TODO 상태의 미션만 1회 수정할 수 있습니다.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="alert alert-light border mb-4" role="alert">
                        <div class="small text-body-secondary">날짜: {{mission.missionDate}}</div>
                        <div class="small text-body-secondary">난이도: {{mission.difficulty}}</div>
                        <div class="small text-body-secondary mb-0">완료된 미션은 수정할 수 없습니다.</div>
                    </div>

                    {{#formError}}
                        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                            {{formError}}
                        </div>
                    {{/formError}}

                    <form action="/missions/{{mission.id}}/edit" method="post">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="missionDate" value="{{mission.missionDate}}">

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label for="content" class="form-label">미션 내용</label>
                            <input id="content" type="text" name="content" value="{{contentValue}}" class="form-control" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <a href="/main" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">취소</a>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">수정하기</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
